I've revised the plan based on your round-0 feedback. The updated file is at /Users/ericalt/Documents/eden/docs/plans/eden-phase-9-web-ui.md. Specifically:
- Added --experiment-config CLI flag and explained drift risk.
- Reordered planner submit into 3 phases (drafting -> ready -> submit) to narrow the unsafe window; documented the residual gap.
- Added --claim-ttl-seconds and pinned that every UI claim sets expires_at.
- Tightened auth: HttpOnly + SameSite=Lax cookie, per-session CSRF token checked on every mutating route, --secure-cookies for TLS deployments, explicit bearer-leak guarantees + test.
- Added --artifacts-dir and a write_proposal_artifact helper that produces file:// URIs.
