- Expanded test plan with test_security_invariants.py, test_partial_write_recovery.py, and explicit cross-request flow tests in test_planner_flow.py.
- Added stranded-claim sanity check, bearer-leak grep, and config-rotation cookie check to verification.
- Risks section reworked accordingly.

